job.title: TSPSC Sr Asst & Jr Asst cum Typist Recruitment 2021 - Apply Online for 127 Vacancies in Telengana
job.body:
Total Vacancies:127

Name of the post:

  • Senior Assistant & Junior Assistant

Description:

The Telangana State Public Service Commission issued a total of 127 vacancies in Telangana for Senior Assistant & Junior Assistant. The online application for these vacancies in Telangana under the TSPSC shall start from 1-04-2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 25-04-2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com.The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for TSPSC Sr Asst. & Jr Asst. cum Typist Recruitment 2021 :

  • Mode of application: Online
  • No information about the application fee.
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 01-04-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 31-05-2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have a degree in B.A, M.COM, B.COM to apply for the post of Senior Assistant & Junior Assistant

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is: 18 years
  • The maximum age required to apply is: 37 years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

TSPSC Sr Asst. & Jr Asst. cum Typist Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Senior Assistant & Junior Assistant  is: 16400-49870 PER MONTH

How to apply for TSPSC Sr Asst & Jr Asst cum Typist Recruitment 2021?

First, visit the official website.

  • Register yourself on the portal of TSPSC
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Senior Assistant & Junior Assistant.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
